{"tid":472853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大畢業典禮疑有人噓國歌　數名學生拒向林鄭鞠躬","createTime":"2017-11-18T15:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T09:45:00.000Z","uid":20058,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df20b8d70b882ba598ba048aa281ab2ce1a3e056","tid":472853,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"近來有香港球迷於港足賽事播放《義勇軍進行曲》時報以噓聲，綜合報道，科技大學今日舉行畢業典禮，播出國歌後有低聲量的疑似噓聲傳出；另有數名畢業生拒絕向身兼校監的特首林鄭月娥鞠躬，或改為背向林鄭對觀眾席鞠躬。<br />\n<br />\n科大發言人表示畢業典禮過程順利，播放國歌後傳出一陣低微而嘈雜的背景人聲，但未知聲音來源，無法確定嘈雜聲的性質。對於有畢業生無向林鄭鞠躬，發言人稱仍在確認中。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄表示，大學生應視乎場合表達意見，並需尊重其他畢業生和家長，希望有一個莊嚴的畢業禮；另稱「港獨」不應在校園出現。<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/235336/%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%80%E6%95%B8%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8B%92%E5%90%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%9E%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F235336%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2585%25B8%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2599%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%259E%25A0%2F&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1LiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=aa68a17f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/235336/%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%80%E6%95%B8%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8B%92%E5%90%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%9E%A0/</a>"},{"pid":"ccd1f6c02bdbdbf12211ae16135ad4c4e8ed1b68","tid":472853,"uid":26065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000eb8d29652a76c75b2694d2d10b04a491044c8","tid":472853,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:15:39.00